Usage Warning:
	1.	This electric rideable suitcase has a maximum speed of 13 km/h and must be used in flat, open, and safe areas. Do not ride in crowded places, on steep slopes, slippery surfaces, or on public roads.
	2.	The following individuals are not advised to use this product:
	•	Children under 14 years old or seniors over 65 years old;
	•	Pregnant women, individuals with limited mobility, or those with heart conditions, high blood pressure, or other health issues;
	•	Users who have not received proper operating instructions or who lack balance ability;
	•	Anyone under the influence of alcohol, medication, or in a poor mental state.
	3.	Riders are strongly advised to wear a helmet and protective gear. Overloading, riding with multiple people standing, or operating with one hand is strictly prohibited.